{
  "texts": [
    "We implemented rank-8 adapters (r=8) for key attention layers and feed-forward networks, with an alpha value of 16 to scale the contribution of the adapters.",
    "This results in 2.4 million trainable parameters (about 0.75% of the base model's size).",
    "The bias term was set to \"none,\" ensuring that no additional bias parameters were learned.",
    "Training DetailsThe model was trained for 1 epoch on the curated dataset, achieving a final training loss of 1.2734.",
    "Training was conducted in a Linux-based environment using CPython 3.12.3."
  ]
}